animeTitle: Dragon Ball Z Movie 10: Kiken na Futari! Super Senshi wa Nemurenai
animeDescription: After his loss to Goku, Broly crash lands and hibernates on earth. After some time, he is awakened by Trunks and Goten, who Broly believes is Kakarott, and goes on a rampage to kill both of them. At the same time, Gohan is on his way to challenge the Legendary Super Saiyan alone.
